  "body": "When the migrate command is run, a config object is created (see https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/blob/develop/packages/core/lib/commands/migrate/run.js#L12-L41) from the input options. Then this options object is used later on. All of the options are used to create the config object and then should probably be discarded in favor of using this config object as all of the information from options should now be available on the config object.\r\n\r\nWe should sort through this, verify that this is true, and update the following code to use the config object only if this is the case.",
